How long do we store your data
We store your data only for the time necessary to ensure that you have effectively benefited from the Services you ordered from our platform, as well as for the period in which you have an active account, with the exception of certain information and thereafter to the extent which applicable law requires us to do so (example the law obliges us to keep accounting records for a period of 10 years).
Your data is stored in our cloud servers, rented from Amazon Web Services EMEA SARL.
